column3: Traffic;Phnom Penh: A car took out a divider at 2:50 am on Saturday
column6: near the Olympic along Sihanouk Boulevard in Veal Vong commune
column8: Phnom Penh.------Two people were injured.------After the incident
column9: the two victims were taken to hospital for treatment. The local authorities took the car to the Traffic Police Headquarters in Phnom Penh to wait for further settlement. ------(1:2)
